Package: SimilaR
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-04-10
Title: Source Code Similarity Detection
Description: Implementation of a novel method based on program dependence graphs to 
    determine R code similarity. A method returns value(s) of similarity from [0,1] as well as binary decision (0 or 1).
URL: http://similar.rexamine.com/
BugReports: http://similar.rexamine.com/
Type: Package
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    stringi
License: GPL (>= 3)
